data.title: Low Cost, Next Day Service
data.meta_description: Skip Hire Windsor. We offer local skip hire in Windsor, Datchet, Eton and surrounding areas.
data.text:
OUR LOCATION

AREAS WE COVER

We believe in putting customer satisfaction above anything else. That’s why we have decided to make our deliveries and collections as swift and as quick as possible so you don’t experience any delays. It’s also why we have made our order and booking system an online service as well as over the phone so you can order in just minutes through our website and even have your skip the same day if possible. We even offer building aggregates as a side order with your skip so that you can have the best and more useful materials at hand at any time whilst underground your building renovations.

Fast Delivery Service

We offer a fast, convenient service. All skips come with this delivery service included in the price. All skips can be delivered the same of next day after the order is placed if needed. Collection is all decided by you also so that we can work around your time schedule.

Book Online in Minutes

You can book online with us in just minutes. We understand that booking over the phone or even just trying to get price quotations over the phone can be a hassle, that’s why we offer an online booking service that is so simple to follow.

Skip Permits Sorted

If you place your skip outside of your own property you will need a permit. No need to worry because we can help you place an order for one. We just contact your local authority and place an order. Prices can vary but they only take around two days to arrive.

All Waste Recycled

We make sure all our waste goes through our recycling process before being sent off anywhere. This ways we can make sure materials that are more than alright can be recycled or reused and that we’re not loading too much rubbish into the landfill.
